reviewText:
This is an amazing game, let me tell you why;

I've been following his developer on his live stream since he started working on stratO and the greatest thing I can say is he has accomplished to create a really hard flying game, it's learning curve is really sharp but once you get used to it it will give you some kind of feeling.

For me, that feeling is tranquility, I start playing it with some drum n' bass music on the background and I can easily play for two hours without stop. It's just the flow it achieves that makes it so great.
